it.polimi.se2018.view

Class View

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.polimi.se2018.utils.Observable
      • it.polimi.se2018.view.View
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Observer, ViewInterface, VisitorView

    public class View
extends Observable
implements VisitorView, ViewInterface
    View offers the CLI service It accepts messages from the server (controller, model), manage them according to instructions in VisitorView and manages to show the end user the contents of the game
